of archery from you.'

82
00:09:46,140 --> 00:09:49,090
'My father is the charioteer
of the great Bhishma.'

83
00:09:50,010 --> 00:09:52,110
'I shall return
but let me assure you'

84
00:09:52,940 --> 00:09:55,920
'that I shall return as the
most skilled archer of India.'

85
00:09:56,070 --> 00:09:58,110
'And I will be superior
to all your disciples.'

86
00:10:00,170 --> 00:10:01,980
