106
00:11:49,070 --> 00:11:52,050
Before the competition begins,
it is crucial to know

107
00:11:53,040 --> 00:11:55,020
as to who the challenger is.

108
00:11:57,810 --> 00:11:58,980
According to the norms
of religion and traditions

109
00:11:59,070 --> 00:12:03,850
a king can fight only with
another king or a prince.

110
00:12:04,810 --> 00:12:05,840
And a prince

111
00:12:05,940 --> 00:12:09,850
can fight only with another
prince or a chief minister.

112
00:12:11,040 --> 00:12:12,780
And a chief minister

113
00:12:12,910 --> 00:12:16,050
can fight only with another
chief minister or a general.

114
00:12:17,970 --> 00:12:19,850
In other words, a warrior

115
00:12:19,870 --> 00:12:20,980
can challenge someone
equal to his rank

116
00:12:21,770 --> 00:12:24,880
or a person who is of
a higher rank than him.

117
00:12:30,010 --> 00:12:31,920
Who are you, lad?

118
00:12:32,870 --> 00:12:35,010
