119
00:12:41,970 --> 00:12:43,920
Before challenging anyone
to a fight

120
00:12:44,770 --> 00:12:45,910
introduce yourself, lad.

121
00:12:52,840 --> 00:12:55,820
Who are you?
You do not seem like a prince.

122
00:12:57,040 --> 00:12:59,020
To which clan of Kshatriya
do you belong?

123
00:13:16,740 --> 00:13:18,720
Do not ask him
that question, Kripacharya.

124
00:13:19,810 --> 00:13:22,950
A warrior who bears such courage
does not deserve to be insulted.

125
00:13:23,010 --> 00:13:24,880
Insult?

126
00:13:24,940 --> 00:13:26,780
Telling about
my lineage and clan

127
00:13:26,840 --> 00:13:28,980
is not insulting to me, sire.

128
00:13:30,970 --> 00:13:32,750
I am

129
00:13:34,840 --> 00:13:36,820
the great Bhishma's charioteer,

130
00:13:37,840 --> 00:13:39,790
Adhirath Sushain's son.

131
00:14:02,670 --> 00:14:03,740
Shudra!

132
00:14:04,710 --> 00:14:05,840
