to learn the art of weaponry?

135
00:14:12,670 --> 00:14:13,740
Yes, I am a charioteer's son!

136
00:14:14,740 --> 00:14:15,840
And I am proud of my father

137
00:14:17,870 --> 00:14:20,750
who provided service to Bhishma
with complete devotion.

138
00:14:25,710 --> 00:14:26,780
I am proud of my mother

139
00:14:28,640 --> 00:14:30,780
who has fortified every inch
of me with her love.

140
00:14:34,770 --> 00:14:35,880
