related to my caste?

149
00:15:06,840 --> 00:15:09,820
No one questions a waterfall
that cleaves through mountains

150
00:15:09,870 --> 00:15:11,680
as to where its source is!

151
00:15:11,770 --> 00:15:14,580
Its strength is its identity!

152
00:15:16,870 --> 00:15:19,880
No one asks the lotus
that is offered to Lord Shiva

153
00:15:20,740 --> 00:15:21,840
as to where it originated!

154
00:15:23,740 --> 00:15:25,840
Its beauty is its clan!

155
00:15:27,870 --> 00:15:31,680
